      "textPreview": "#F8F8F8\n          \n          \n            \n              AI at Adobe.\n              Give your teams the productivity tools and always-on insights to deliver true personalization at scale with Adobe’s AI solutions.\n            \n            \n              \n                \n                \n                \n                \n              \n            \n          \n        \n        \n          \n            #F8F8F8\n          \n          \n            \n              Explore products.\n              \n                \n                  \n                    \n                    \n                    \n        "
    },
    {
