      "textPreview": "#F8F8F8\n          \n          \n            \n              Accelerated document workflows that deliver more impact.\n              Organize documents into a connected, insight-rich hub. Adobe Acrobat Studio combines trusted PDF tools with AI-powered insights, secure knowledge spaces, and standout content creation.\n            \n            \n              \n                \n                \n                \n                \n              \n            \n          \n        \n        \n          \n            #F8F8F8\n          \n          \n            \n              Explore products.\n              \n        "
